# Toolchain

- **Lint & format**: [Biome](https://biomejs.dev/). Run `npm run check` (read-only) or `npm run lint` (fix where safe). Prefer `npm run format` for formatting-only passes.
- **Tests**: Vitest (`npm run test`, `npm run test.watch`). Use `describe` / `it` / `expect` globals; mocks use `vi` from globals (see `vitest.config.ts`).
- **Build**: Rolldown bundles from `src/index.ts`; TypeScript declarations are emitted via `tsc -p tsconfig.build.json`. Do not bring back Rollup unless there is an explicit requirement.
